installationInstructions.author: Linda from ST AUGUSTINE, FL
installationInstructions.title: Latch for ice box door broke off
installationInstructions.content: Received replacement part. There is a cover over the ice box latch. Pried it off with a screwdriver head. Took the broken latch off replaced new latch to cover and replaced on the door.
